KJr_UB87GwA">Lưu Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%C3%AA-Khang/T%E1%BA%B7ng-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i-nh%E1%BA%ADp-qu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-13/poem-q2p7q2Zh9VsAee9FWep-6w">Tặng tú tài nhập quân kỳ 13 - 贈秀才入軍其十三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%C3%AA-Khang/author-ktzrFwfJkeyrhgg3ubmVdQ">Kê Khang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/%E1%BB%A8c-Long-%C4%90%E1%BB%99i-s%C6%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-wHLLFlFKOePG_bbxU9ruXA">Ức Long Đội sơn kỳ 2 - 憶龍隊山其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-gi%E1%BA%A3i-t%E1%BB%AD-phu-ph%E1%BB%A5/poem-nvWXldPQFCgPzVvH2hpTWw">Vương giải tử phu phụ - 王解子夫婦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/author-WRSP543j56aeSlO4dZfsBQ">Ngô Gia Kỷ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
